  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Public Engagement Rep",
  "description": "<h2>🎉 Public Engagement Rep</h2><p>✨ Want a role that gets you out, talking to people, and learning real-world skills?</p><p>At <strong>Vision Organisation</strong>, you’ll be part of live, on-ground campaigns where brands meet people face-to-face. This role is all about communication, confidence, and growing through hands-on experience in marketing and sales.</p><h2>💼 What You’ll Be Doing</h2><ul><li><p>👋 Engage customers through friendly, face-to-face conversations</p></li><li><p>📣 Support brand activities at events, roadshows, and outreach campaigns</p></li><li><p>💬 Build communication and customer engagement skills on the job</p></li><li><p>🤝 Work closely with your team to deliver smooth, successful campaigns</p></li></ul><h2>🚀 What You’ll Get</h2><ul><li><p>🎓 Full training provided — no prior experience needed</p></li><li><p>📈 Performance-based growth with clear development pathways</p></li><li><p>🌍 Opportunities to take part in different campaigns and locations</p></li><li><p>🤝 Ongoing mentorship, guidance, and learning support</p></li></ul><h2>🙌 This Role Is Great For You If You</h2><ul><li><p>Enjoy meeting and talking to new people</p></li><li><p>Are open to learning and trying new things</p></li><li><p>Are positive, reliable, and team-oriented</p></li><li><p>Like active, on-the-ground work (not desk-based)</p></li></ul><h2>📩 How to Apply</h2><p>Interested in gaining hands-on experience in public engagement, marketing, and sales?</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507</p>",
